into a red bowling ball?

1:12:27.977 --> 1:12:31.346
O.M.G.

1:13:00.009 --> 1:13:01.509
Take that!

1:13:12.889 --> 1:13:13.821
Gotcha.

1:13:19.963 --> 1:13:21.662
Yay. Oh.

1:14:18.521 --> 1:14:19.654
Yeah.

1:14:21.791 --> 1:14:22.723
Chief!

1:14:28.798 --> 1:14:30.731
Let him go, let him go.

1:14:32.469 --> 1:14:33.701
Brightheart!

1:14:54.624 --> 1:14:57.258
It's coming. Get back,
get away from the tracks.

1:15:03.099 --> 1:15:05.500
