of us have a chance.

1:16:50.673 --> 1:16:52.640
I see what she is trying to do

1:16:52.642 --> 1:16:56.143
but she has a one percent
chance of success.

1:16:56.145 --> 1:16:57.845
There's got to be another way.

1:16:57.847 --> 1:17:00.247
I'm open to suggestion.

1:17:03.252 --> 1:17:06.988
Firefly Action Brigade,
I believe in you.

1:17:19.936 --> 1:17:23.838
On my count, put your
shields around Brightheart.

1:17:37.687 --> 1:17:38.419
